### Answers CRUD

### 1. Crear Answer (POST /answers)
# @name createAnswer
POST {{baseUrl}}/answers
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "questionId": "{{questionId}}",
  "answer_text": "Lima",
  "is_correct": true
}

# @after response
# > {"answerId":"{{$response.body#/id}}"}

### 2. Obtener Answers por Question (GET /answers/question/{{questionId}})
# @name getAnswersByQuestion
GET {{baseUrl}}/answers/question/{{questionId}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 3. Obtener Answer por id (GET /answers/{{answerId}})
# @name getAnswerById
GET {{baseUrl}}/answers/{{answerId}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 4. Actualizar Answer (PUT /answers/{{answerId}})
# @name updateAnswer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/answers/{{answerId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "answer_text": "Ciudad de Lima",
  "is_correct": true
}

### 5. Borrar Answer (DELETE /answers/{{answerId}})
# @name deleteAnswer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/answers/{{answerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
